A comprehensive and holistic community outreach campaign at different levels:  
1. A series of Polkadot theme meet-ups and in Nordic and Scandinavian countries.   
2. A developer only target conference in-depth discuss Polkadot and substrate   
3. A branded hackathon focus on Polkadot and substrate development, as part of the annual European largest hackathon, 
https://www.hackjunction.com.
